CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

October 8, 2008

[Cite as 10/08/2008 Case Announcements, 2008-Ohio-5229.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2007-1832. Roe v. Planned Parenthood Southwest Ohio Region.

Hamilton App. No. C-060557, 173 Ohio App.3d 414, 2007-0hio-4318. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Hamilton County. Upon consideration of appellees’ expedited motion to prohibit use of proposed exhibit at oral argument, It is ordered by the court that the motion is granted.

Donovan, J., dissents. Mary E. Donovan, J., sitting for O’Connor, J.
